definitions.definition: Any meteor of a meteor shower that appears to radiate from the constellation Leo in November.

main_definition: Any meteor of a meteor shower that appears to radiate from the constellation Leo in November.

definitions.definition: A male given name , a transliteration of a common East Slavic name (notably that of the first two Ukrainian presidents, Leonid Kravchuk and Leonid Kuchma, as well as Soviet leader Leonid Brezhnev).

main_definition: A male given name , a transliteration of a common East Slavic name (notably that of the first two Ukrainian presidents, Leonid Kravchuk and Leonid Kuchma, as well as Soviet leader Leonid Brezhnev).
